Seasonal change of clock settings

"DST", "Daylight savings", and "Summer time" redirect here. For the film, see [Daylight Savings (film)](/Daylight_Savings_(film)). For the season, see [Summer](/Summer). For other uses, see [DST (disambiguation)](/DST_(disambiguation)) and [Summertime](/Summertime_(disambiguation)).

